pageContext.claim: “Women for Kavanaugh, and many others who support this very good man, are gathering all over Capitol Hill in preparation for a 3-5 P.M. VOTE. It is a beautiful thing to see - and they are not paid professional protesters who are handed expensive signs. Big day for America!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump suggests that the people protesting Kavanaugh are "paid professional protesters" but that's false.
